r bases. Finally we make\nexemplary computations to demonstrate the conspicuous difference between\nGr\\\"obner bases and the new type of bases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Jan 2021 06:29:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-12"}
