e moves through the region; the\nresidual error order $\\mathcal{O}(t^{-1})$ from a $\\overline\\partial$ equation.\nOur results provide a verification of the soliton resolution conjecture and\nasymptotic stability of N-soliton solutions for three-wave equation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Jan 2021 09:52:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 May 2021 12:06:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-11"}
